{"tid":1624611,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［我地唔係要搞破壞] 後生仔女幫助清潔姐姐鏟走地上玻璃碎","createTime":"2019-10-05T04:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T07:48:59.000Z","uid":259980,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"472c2f7e7f905d467d086f010f96e1f962e64d23","tid":1624611,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XsztOBB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXsztOBB.jpg&h=32398be1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地並唔係想搞破壞或者為難任何人<br />\n我地同所有街坊一樣好愛香港<br />\n好愛自己社區<br />\n只係受極權壓迫<br />\n無還擊之力嘅我地<br />\n只可以對嗰d幫助極權政府嘅企業、商店<br />\n進行針對性打擊<br />\n令佢地承受經濟損失<br />\n希望各位體諒<br />\n我地承諾係香港人勝利嘅一日<br />\n會用盡所有心機重建自己嘅家園<br />\n令香港變返做佢應有嘅樣子"},{"pid":"18feb20e2a533372cd22c340f368d0e46d896b1d","tid":1624611,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:22:09.000Z","msg":"香港人"},{"pid":"a5c3be947810ae1570c167cad0c00031919e7a7d","tid":1624611,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:22:19.000Z","msg":"反抗"},{"pid":"ed3b4cbb1103ed599c09efa99c95c5370d6d4385","tid":1624611,"uid":79228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:31:29.000Z","msg":"小心唔好送頭 萬事小心"},{"pid":"8a745e87766546a67172e1c411c4502d6234a788","tid":1624611,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:41:35.000Z","msg":"漸變豬應該係党員<br />\n有 walkie &amp; waist bag"},{"pid":"b0a0c207b8391f40d91f8f8705805cfecd7ffd2f","tid":1624611,"uid":258003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:48:59.000Z","msg":"要做啲嘢表示自己係愛香港<br />\n清理嘅手足good job<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}